data.description: Investment potential in the Palisades neighborhood of Lake Oswego. A project you can live in as you go, or flip a high-end home. New dishwasher, double oven, washer & dryer. Clean lines and an open flow with tons of windows making it light and bright, providing a beautiful private backdrop out every window. Open kitchen/dine/den areas. Massive bonus/family room with wet-bar, fireplace, deck and built-ins. Huge laundry room with option for wine cellar. Spacious bedrooms with California Closet organizing systems. Oversize double garage with a flat driveway, storage galore and AC. Palisades Boat/Lake Easement, Swim Parks, Greentree Pool and award winning schools. Creative lending options. This is a fantastic opportunity!
